officials and for widespread wildcats one over grievance 
procedures that idled 70000 miners in 1975 which the umw leaders 
appeared to be unable to control 
he worked to focus the memberships efforts less on internal 
disputes and more on fighting the companies he won broad new powers 
from the membership including the unions first strike fund and the 
authority to call selective strikes 
