permits from their local police stations before chinese guards 
outside foreign embassies allow them to enter to apply for visas 
according to reports in the official media over the weekend the 
new rules invalidate all permits issued before tuesday through 
monday chinese could still use the old permits to enter embassy 
grounds but as of tuesday the old permits were not good for even 
that 
