fleet ministry as saying there was fog when the ship hit the iceberg 
only the emergency team will remain on the maxim gorky to fight 
for the life of the ship after they arrive the soviet rescuers 
must determine the character of the damage the possibility of 
eliminating it and make decisions about repair izvestia said 
the cruise ship was built in west germany in 1969 and sold to the 
soviets in 1974 
