pg13 
 
stealing home with its baseball underpinnings is a sweet 
little tale of comingofage in middleclass america a place with 
proms and summer at the beach 
its good stuff for a family saturday night viewing but you 
might need a bit of parental guidance for the younger set 
mark harmon stars as the wouldbe baseball hero and jodie foster 
